title: Metallica - Donington England 6-6-2004 SOUNDBOARD FLAC
description:
Metallica - Download England 2004-6-6
SOUNDBOARD AUDIO



The Ecstasy of Gold 
(Ennio Morricone song)
Battery 
(with Dave Lombardo)
The Four Horsemen 
(with Dave Lombardo)

(with Joey Jordison)
Creeping Death 
(with Joey Jordison)
Seek & Destroy 
(with Joey Jordison)

(with Flemming Larsen (Lars' Drum Tech))
Wherever I May Roam 
(with Joey Jordison)
Last Caress 
(Misfits cover) (with Joey Jordison)

(with Joey Jordison) (followed by guitar solo)

(with Joey Jordison)
Enter Sandman 
(with Joey Jordison)



Note: Lars suffers a breakdown and misses this show. Up until this point, he was the only member of Metallica to perform at every show. While other members (Kirk, Rob, Jason, Cliff, Dave and Ron) never missed any shows, each was, of course, never always in Metallica. James missed three shows in July 2000.
